{
  "stem": "471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was the Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you see, like, some of them, you know, they were very, very, very primitive, you know, limited.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's put this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the first funny thing, what happened to me, when the war broked out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, when I start to see the soldiers, and what people were saying, how everybody was running away, I start to realize that the names-- the-- the names-- the names are not German.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That the Germans are here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whatever I have seen from before, a year or two years before, how they, you know, all the families, they had to go to the railroad station, pick up the family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he threw them all-- all German Jew, what they came-- how-- [POLISH], how do you say that?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came from--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- their roots are from Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because eventually, there's no German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the Polish Jew was emigrating to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He threw them over the-- over the border, the way it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 19--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the families and everything, some of them, they were in their pajamas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in 1938.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39 Already.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He threw all the-- all the-- all the Jews from Germany, whatever he could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember like today, the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Jewish Community Center, they really took care of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took care of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I knew people had to go to the station, take a family, a temporary-- you know, until they could locate them and give them food and money.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had practically in pajamas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, this I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
